00:06:44.066 --> 00:06:49.134
The first iteration of the Underground, of the tube, as it's now called, had

00:06:49.154 --> 00:06:54.844
wooden carriages that were lit by gas lanterns and pulled by steam trains.

00:06:55.654 --> 00:07:00.174
It wouldn’t have been particularly comfortable, but it was revolutionary.

00:07:01.624 --> 00:07:05.434
