Now, to finish off this short exploration into the history of the tube,

00:15:24.252 --> 00:15:28.442
I have five pieces of trivia, facts, about the London underground.

00:15:29.682 --> 00:15:35.042
So, first up: if you are on the Central line, which unsurprisingly goes through

00:15:35.052 --> 00:15:40.902
