00:16:33.232 --> 00:16:39.602
Leicester Square and Covent Garden, which is on the Piccadilly line, and is just 300 metres.

00:16:40.462 --> 00:16:45.366
It’s so close, in fact, that there is no point taking the tube from Leicester

