00:17:00.916 --> 00:17:05.576
And finally, our fifth fact, in a single year trains on the

00:17:05.576 --> 00:17:10.866
London Underground travel a staggering 83.6 million kilometres.

00:17:11.586 --> 00:17:17.444
It’s quite the journey from the gas-light steam-powered trains that made that first journey in 1863.

00:17:19.134 --> 00:17:23.314
So, there you go, a brief but hopefully interesting

00:17:23.314 --> 00:17:25.994
